{"tid":604518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車Cam直擊】婦人大埔道依燈號過路 遭疑衝燈紅Van撞死","createTime":"2018-03-24T18:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T01:17:06.000Z","uid":7812,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"294786e4d92da853abc4c6161fe02f6b4f9c45df","tid":604518,"uid":7812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T18:25:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180324&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57990810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180324%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57990810&d=1LdOpM0nCRdJpwOlqmJwtqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=7d25882d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180324%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57990810&h=3c876988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180324&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57990810</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晨深水埗大埔道一輛紅色小巴撞斃一名過路婦人，《蘋果》取得一段拍攝到車禍經過的車cam片，片段所見當時女事主在交通燈位，正依燈號以正常步速橫過大埔道，惟涉事紅色小巴沿大埔道快線落斜往深水埗，疑衝紅燈將婦人猛撞至翻滾幾圈倒地，她當場昏迷，一雙波鞋也飛脫。<br />\n<br />\n現場是薩凡納藝術設計學院對開紅綠燈位，上址交通燈是跨越上、落斜兩方，上斜有3條行車線，落斜則有兩條行車線，中間有安全島分隔；而現場燈號是一致，即上、落斜兩方均為紅或綠燈。<br />\n<br />\n從車cam片段所見，當時婦人由上斜方向的左邊步出馬路，當時上斜行車燈號為紅燈，並有兩部車輛在燈位前等候，婦人行過安全島後，走出落斜方向僅行出2步，即遭一輛落斜的紅色小巴撞倒，將她猛撞至翻滾幾圈倒地。片段所見，小巴的車速頗快，疑有人衝燈肇禍。"},{"pid":"8de9a9bf4ed68de678b9dc912d84ae7d139495f4","tid":604518,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T18:32:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f741483b8b1d48fcf9d2085f99daea8a5e5fc972","tid":604518,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T18:33:51.000Z","msg":"又一單 今年好似好多交通命案"},{"pid":"1301dfad4f6d7094c7c37db06a23414b61cda3db","tid":604518,"uid":7812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f741483b8b1d48fcf9d2085f99daea8a5e5fc972","tid":604518,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T18:33:51.000Z","msg":"又一單 今年好似好多交通命案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T18:55:24.000Z","msg":"真係好多 日日都有 仲要唔止一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e669b42a8c5a665368e129c7fb0b75c53cd170d0","tid":604518,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T19:04:00.000Z","msg":"坐七個月又一條好漢唔撞就笨"},{"pid":"2daa4b3a9d988cea9b896cd80b4252dddce4d2df","tid":604518,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T19:06:57.000Z","msg":"紅van真係好撚多事"},{"pid":"53facd8c4d96b0ad5f506b136ad0b346a33dc1e5","tid":604518,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T19:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec618aada764767b8d2eb2daf26307aa638f2357","tid":604518,"uid":88797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T19:17:37.000Z","msg":"隔離po又係benz衝燈撞人<br />\n唔小心揸車害死人"},{"pid":"83fd3fc80a9088b91487352d441508d9ffc253f3","tid":604518,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T01:17:06.000Z","msg":"66歲撞死68歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保皇又少2票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}